name: Vessels Report
query:
select 
 `tabBooking Request`.`eta_date` as "ETA DATE:Date",
 `tabBooking Request`.`vessel_type` as "Vessel Type:Link/Vessel Type:120",
 `tabBooking Request`.`vessel` as "Vessel:Link/Vessels:120",
 `tabVessels`.`vessel_gross_tonnage` as "GRT::120",
 `tabBooking Request`.`eta_pilot_date` as "Achorage Date/Time:Date",
 `tabBooking Request`.`mooring_date` as "Mooring Date/Time:Date",
 `tabBooking Request`.`unmooring_date` as "UN-Mooring Date/Time:Date",
`tabBooking Request`.`cargo_ops_start_date` as "Ops Start Date/Time:Date",
`tabBooking Request`.`cargo_ops_completed_date` as "Ops End Date/Time:Date"
from
`tabBooking Request`, `tabVessels`, `tabCargo Booking Manifest Table`
where
`tabBooking Request`.vessel = `tabVessels`.vessel
and
`tabBooking Request`.name = `tabCargo Booking Manifest Table`.parent
